cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image classification and detection of errors in classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of adversarial attacks also suggests a potential connection to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also discusses the potential security implications of adversarial attacks, which could place it in the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category. Finally, the use of image transformations suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM) as well.
